title: IMSI TurboFloorPlan 2016 Pro Portable
description:
TurboFloorPlan Home and Landscaping Design 2016 Pro Portable

image

1. your computer MUST support virtual technology to use this portable.

Few home design software programs offer the user-ability and feature set that 
TurboFloorPlan 3D Home and Landscape Pro offers. This user-friendly house building 
software will have beginning home designers drawing custom floor plans within the 
hour and yet has all the tools to keep advanced users satisfied.

This house plan software can help plan your home remodel with real-life 
applications, such as a cost estimator and electrical and plumbing planning tools 
that are essential for your planning.

Overall Utility

This is one of the easiest-to-use home remodeling software products that we 
reviewed. Drawing a floor plan from scratch is easy with the QuickStart menu. With 
QuickStart, rooms are labeled and color-coded for you above your blank floor plan. 
As you add rooms to your custom floor plan, a 3D model will automatically generate.

If you want to furnish your custom floor plan quickly, there are editable room 
templates that you can drag and drop into empty rooms. The editable room templates 
include finished kitchens, bedrooms, living areas and more. These room templates can
help give you ideas on how to style each room. The templates are editable, so you 
can change any details that you donâ€™t like.

Navigating through your 3D model isnâ€™t difficult with TurboFloorPlan Pro. The 
taskbar atop your screen is clear and concise when navigating between 2D and 3D 
views. You can choose to walkthrough your 3D home, take an aerial tour or view your 
entire 3D model layout from above without the roof, also called a dollhouse view. 
All of these views are easy to select and control.

Interior Design & Kitchen

While looking at your 2D floor plan, you will notice a list of tabs at the top of 
your window. You can get as detailed as you want with your floor plan by adding 
electrical, plumbing, HVAC and more. These tools, along with the cost estimator, 
become quintessential for real-life remodeling, helping you plan and budget your 
remodel before you attempt the real thing.

One construction quality this program has that few other home design software 
products have is the ability to curve walls. Curved walls are a great way to add 
unique character to your home. You can also add plenty of character to your property
by changing the topography of your property. You can add hills, valleys and much 
more. To put the finishing touches on your yard, there is a fencing tool, which you 
can use to customize and add the final touches to your yard.

Construction & Landscaping

The plant library alone offers thousands of different trees, shrubs, flowers and 
other plant life to facilitate your yard. With the topography tools and this large 
plant library, you can design the yard that youâ€™ve always wanted.

The object library offers thousands of options and combinations of both indoor and 
outdoor furniture, appliances, flooring, light fixtures and more. There are hundreds
of cabinet combinations to choose from that match any decorative style.

When you add anything from the object library, you first have to add them to your 2D
plan. We were unable to drag and drop objects from the object library straight to 
the 3D model. Other software we reviewed allows you to do both, so you donâ€™t have to
keep toggling between 2D and 3D views.

Help & Support

There are many video tutorials online and an in-program manual, which you can use to
help you start using TurboFloorPlan Pro. If you encounter any problems with your 
software, you can contact IMSI Design via email and telephone.

Summary

TurboFloorPlan Home and Landscaping Pro is one of the easiest home design programs 
to use that we reviewed. It offers many tools to help you plan your home renovation 
including cost estimators and electrical and plumbing planners. Whether you are a 
beginner or advanced user of house planning software, TurboFloorPlan Pro can help 
you plan a redesign of your home
